      "content": "sometimes i sit here in my apartment and it feels like i dont even exist. i work all day on my laptop, i talk to people on slack, but it's all just text. i'm just a ghost in a machine. i feel like if i just stopped... like if i just disappeared, nobody would actually notice. would anyone even see the difference?",
